OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe east
OL,6,Fwill be dry with a few clear periods
OL,7,Fovernight. Dumfries and Galloway will
OL,8,Fbe cloudy with some patchy rain,
OL,9,Fmainly over the hills. Mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FEdinburgh, Lothian and
OL,12,Feastern Borders mainly dry with some
OL,13,Foccasional brightness. Dumfries,
OL,14,FGalloway and western Borders cloudy
OL,15,Fwith rain at times. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
